### 1. `package.json` (Dependências e Scripts)
Este arquivo define as dependências iniciais do ecossistema, incluindo ícones (`lucide-react`) e o framework de compilação rápida `vite`.
```json
{
  "name": "sistema-prontuario-academico",
  "private": true,
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "type": "module",
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "vite",
    "build": "vite build",
    "preview": "vite preview"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "lucide-react": "^0.354.0",
    "react": "^18.2.0",
    "react-dom": "^18.2.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/react": "^18.2.66",
    "@types/react-dom": "^18.2.22",
    "@vitejs/plugin-react": "^4.2.1",
    "autoprefixer": "^10.4.18",
    "postcss": "^8.4.35",
    "tailwindcss": "^3.4.1",
    "vite": "^5.1.6"
  }
}
